OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will be
OL,6,Fcloudy through the evening with rain
OL,7,Fslowly spreading east, Rain turning to
OL,8,Fsnow on the hills before clearing
OL,9,Fovernight, which may allow some frost
OL,10,Fto develop.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FA cold and quite cloudy start
OL,13,Fwith some frost. Then a dry and
OL,14,Fincreasingly sunny day, but feeling
OL,15,Fcooler than recent days.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FDry
OL,18,Fand bright on Saturday. Mostly dry
OL,19,Fwith variable cloud and bright spells
OL,20,Fon Sunday and Monday, but a chance of
OL,21,Fthe odd spell of rain.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
